# macros/

Place custom Jinja macros here.

## Conventions

- One macro per file, named after the macro
- Use `{{ project_name }}_` prefix for project-specific macros to avoid conflicts
- Document each macro with a docstring comment

## Example

```sql
{% macro cents_to_dollars(column_name) %}
    ({{ column_name }} / 100.0)::numeric(18, 2)
{% endmacro %}
```
